{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889160/extras/steam_desc_logo_final.png?t=1732931677\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Craggenrock</strong> is a crafting shop management game taking place on a remote island after a great disaster. You play as Arlo, a young crafter seeking a name of his own replacing his former crafting master in the mining town of Pareho.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Skill-Based Crafting</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889160/extras/crafting.gif?t=1732931677\" />Craft quality equipment on your workstations, each with its own minigame. <strong>Time your presses right</strong> and make better equipment; plus, it\u2019s quicker too! Experiment with <strong>700+ recipes</strong> to stock your shop. With a high enough crafting level, you can skip the minigames to save energy manning your shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Shopkeeping</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889160/extras/shopkeeping.gif?t=1732931677\" />Put items on display, open your shop and watch as customers flood in. <strong>Price items by quality</strong> and adjust to your customers\u2019 needs. Out of things to sell? Take the mantle of the customer and shop for <strong>200+ materials</strong> from other merchants in town, some of which are <strong>seasonal</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Jobs and Haggling</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When selling things aren\u2019t enough, <strong>accept jobs from adventurers</strong> for custom gear. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Still not enough money? Merchant prices are too high and job offers are too low? Time to haggle! <strong>Negotiate with your customers or fellow merchants</strong> for that sweet win-win price spot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">(Build Your Own) Reputation</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889160/extras/reputation.gif?t=1732931677\" />Manage your shop\u2019s reputation by <strong>fulfilling jobs on time, pricing items just right and crafting quality equipment</strong> fit for your renown. Townspeople and adventurers might offer (or decline) jobs and adjust their budgets based on your reputation!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Other things to look forward to:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Town events</strong> that influence material availability, supply and prices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Create the recipe</strong> to recreate the mysterious new material that appeared in town</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889160/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732931677","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889160/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732931677","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889160/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732931677","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889160/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732931677","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889160/extras/steam_desc_logo_final.png?t=1732931677\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Craggenrock</strong> is a crafting shop management game taking place on 